author: Michel G
title: God value - you know what you get
text: Stayed there for a stopover before a trip to Luxembourg. The place is just fine. You get what you expect. The room was quite large, very clean and quiet. All I normally need was there. Breakfast was fine. A good place in the neighbourhood.
